<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Attiva il tuo account AssetTrack</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f4f4f4; font-family:Arial, sans-serif;">
    <div style="width:100%; padding:20px; background-color:#f4f4f4;">
      <div style="max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; background-color:#ffffff; padding:40px; border-radius:8px; text-align:center; border:1px solid #5d80ab;">
        {{> header}}
        <div style="text-align:left;">
          <div style="font-size:24px; color:#5d80ab; margin-bottom:20px;">Attiva il tuo account</div>
          <div style="font-size:16px; color:#555555; margin-bottom:30px; line-height:1.5; text-align:left;">
            <p style="margin:0;">Ciao!</p>
            <p style="margin:0;">Sei stato invitato a unirti al workspace {{companyName}} di AssetTrack. Per iniziare a utilizzare il sistema, attiva il tuo account facendo clic sul pulsante o sul link sottostante</p>
            <p style="margin:0; margin-top: 10px;">
              <strong>
                <a href="{{activationLink}}" style="color:#5d80ab; text-decoration:none;">{{activationLink}}</a>
              </strong>
            </p>
            <p style="margin:0; margin-top: 10px;">Il link di invito Ã¨ valido fino al {{expirationDate}} alle {{expirationTime}}.</p>
            <p style="margin:0;">Grazie</p>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:20px;margin-top:75px;">
            <a href="{{activationLink}}" style="display:inline-block; padding:12px 24px; font-size:16px; color:#ffffff; background-color:#5d80ab; text-decoration:none; border-radius:4px;">Attiva il tuo Account</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        {{> footer}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>